        "isa_rec1": "<strong>Those who plan to use a large sum within 3~5 years:</strong> It is suitable for preparing short/medium-term purpose funds such as marriage funds and house preparation. You only need to fulfill the duty participation period of 3 years.",
        "isa_rec2": "<strong>Those who have filled the pension savings account limit:</strong> It is the best alternative when you need additional tax-saving means after filling the pension savings/IRP limit. Additional tax credit is also possible when switching maturity funds to a pension account.",
